The paper deals with the use of relay selection to improve the security and reliability of cognitive radio systems, which involves topics related to information theory (cs.IT), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), computer networks and communications (cs.CR), multimedia (cs.MM), and systems and control (cs.SY). The paper specifically focuses on the selection of the best relay for assisting the secondary transmission, which is a key aspect of cognitive radio systems and falls under the purview of these sub-categories.
